headline: Dossier™ Announces Retail Expansion with National Distribution at Target
summary: Dossier, the perfume house for the next generation, is now at Target, one of the U.S.'s largest shopping destinations. Select bestsellers and exclusive new launches across the brand's Impressions and Originals Collections are available to shop at participating Target stores nationwide and online at Target.com.

headline: Target: An Undervalued Defensive Retail Play With Long-Term Upside
